     H            Y.
     F** FCCR20 ****************************************
     F*   KANBAN M/F                                   *
     F*                                                *
     F* DATE (CODING):K.OKACHI        1997.10.16       *
     F**************************************** FCCR20 **
     FFCCPW20 CF  E                    WORKSTN
     FFCCPL11 IF  E           K        DISK
     E                    ER      1  20 60
      *
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80B4SKHZ
     I                                        1   40B4SKYY
     I                                        5   60B4SKMM
     I                                        7   80B4SKDD
     I            DS
     I                                        1   80B4SRHZ
     I                                        1   40B4SRYY
     I                                        5   60B4SRMM
     I                                        7   80B4SRDD
      *
     C           *ENTRY    PLIST
     C                     PARM           NURI    2
     C                     MOVE NURI      @RUI    20
     C                     MOVE NURI      #MM
      *
     C                     SETON                     50
     C           STEP1     TAG
     C                     EXFMTFCCPW201
     C                     SETOF                     010203
     C                     SETOF                     040599
     C                     SETOF                     50
      *
     C           *INKA     IFEQ '1'
     C                     SETON                     LR
     C                     RETRN
     C                     END
      *
     C           #MM       IFLT 1
     C           #MM       ORGT 12
     C                     MOVE ER,01     MSG
     C                     SETON                     0199
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C           #NONY     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,02     MSG
     C                     SETON                     029950
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C           #KOJ      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,03     MSG
     C                     SETON                     0399
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C           #UKE      IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,04     MSG
     C                     SETON                     0499
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C           #SBAN     IFEQ *BLANK
     C                     MOVE ER,05     MSG
     C                     SETON                     0599
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
      *
     C                     MOVE #NONY     WNONY   40
     C           KEY1      KLIST
     C                     KFLD           @RUI
     C                     KFLD           WNONY
     C                     KFLD           #KOJ
     C                     KFLD           #UKE
     C                     KFLD           #SBAN
      *
     C                     SETOF                     10
     C           KEY1      CHAINFCCPL111             10
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '1'
     C                     MOVE ER,06     MSG
     C                     SETON                     010203
     C                     SETON                     040599
     C                     SETOF                     80
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C           *IN10     IFEQ '0'
     C           B4SKBN    IFEQ 'D'
     C           B4SKHZ    ANDLE*DATE
     C                     MOVE ER,06     MSG
     C                     SETON                     010203
     C                     SETON                     040599
     C                     GOTO STEP1
     C                     END
     C                     MOVE B4MHN1    #UHN1
     C                     MOVE B4MHN2    #UHN2
     C                     MOVE B4MHN3    #UHN3
     C                     MOVE B4MHN4    #UHN4
     C                     SETON                     80
     C                     END
     C                     GOTO STEP1
**  ER
E-01 INPUT ERROR (MONTH)
E-02 INPUT ERROR (RECEIVING CO.)
E-03 INPUT ERROR (FACTORY)
E-04 INPUT ERROR (DOCK CODE)
E-05 INPUT ERROR (KANBAN NO.)
E-06 INPUT DATA NOT FOUND
